    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 1 for MRL 2. Overall credibility body of evidence is sufficient to support regulatory submission for Class II CPB device hemolysis prediction.",
